{"type":null,"faqId":45238,"title":"有些场景会出现智能截屏误触发，导致屏幕无法操作，如何减少指关节智能截屏误触发？","answer":"<p>如下场景容易发生误触发：\n<br>\n1.\t来电是振动模式 2. 音乐外放 3. 闹铃振动 4. 播放视频外放。\n<br>\n如果是来电振动或者闹铃振动，建议用户关闭振动(\"设置 &gt; 声音 &gt; 点击时振动\"，关闭开关)或者关闭智能截屏功能(进入\"设置 &gt; 手势空控制 &gt; 智能截屏\"，能够查看到智能截屏开关，点击就可以正常关闭)。\n<br>\n如果是音乐外放或者播放视频外放误触发，建议用户关机智能截屏。\n<br>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"738","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442451579000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"截屏,误触","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}